lead_paragraph: General Montgomery's dramatic victory at the Mareth Line has so centered attention on land operations in Tunisia that we are apt to overlook its effect on the Mediterranean sea-front. Yet it will have a profound effect on that front which should eventually be felt from Gibraltar to Alexandria.
